      "amount": "to taste",
      "notes": ""
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut cream and coconut milk in a saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add mashed taro, minced garlic, red chilli flakes, and sugar. Mix well.",
    "Stir in vinegar continuously until it starts to boil and thicken slightly.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let simmer for about 5 minutes until the mixture thickens further and coats the back of a spoon.",
    "Serve warm or at room temperature as a snack or accompaniment."
